      "description": "Tribute to VVS: we shall never be able to statistically explain to the\r\n20-20 generation- why Laxman is very very special. How the value of each\r\nrun he made is perhaps more valuable than the thousands more that sachin\r\nDravid, Ganguly have made. How his epic 281 changed the face of Indian\r\ncricket forever. How his recent scores of 74 and 96 were more special than\r\nmany of the hundreds. We shall cherish the fact that we enjoyed cricket in an era VVS played. RESPECT & REVERENCE to the great man."
