      "title": "Photos",
      "description": "Dirty politics started the figure of 65k crore which actually ought to have been much much higher was scripted (as predicted by @[613582044:2048:Roopendra Narayan Roy] in a comment) and here it comes. \n\nI can understand RaGa having to do all this to stay relevant but RRR dancing to the script should be shocking to those who thought he was the solution to all the problems India faced. In the hindsight, Modi was right in showing him the door as RBI governor."
