      "title": "Photos",
      "description": "Nobel Laureate Abhijit Banerjee follows the footsteps of RRR (refer my previous post here https://tinyurl.com/y8ykcepg). There is little doubt left that these 3 (3rd being Amartya Sen) have chosen to become pawns in the hands of a political party and their opinions cannot/should not to be taken at face value. \n\nIt's really painful that individuals of such high calibre, name and fame allow themselves to be exploited for narrow political gains or may be this too is a new normal."
