      "title": "Photos",
      "description": "How our gen is unique in so many ways \n\nWe are the last generation which has seen life \n\n- from doordarshan to satellite to OTT\n- from one landline phone to 2 sim cards in every mobile\n- life before and after not only internet but we also see life before and after AI\n- india winning 2 ODI WC \n\nwe even saw thru the corona kaal but yet in the twilight years of our life we shall be most proud that we saw this day when 496 years of wait got over, \nhow many generations before us waited to see this day but we have been the chosen one, much of our gen next is underprepared to realise the enormity of this piece of history that they are seeing pass by (busy on their phones) and in many ways our previous generation and we are the fortunate ones to experience, understand and realise the value of what we have been witnessed.\n\nLet the happiness, the celebrations and the after effects of witnessing such a historic event continue to linger in our hearts."
